This extensions adds GTALens links for jobs and users' profiles on Rockstar Games Social Club website. GTALens.com - modern Social Club alternative - allows you to view more info about each job, browse hidden jobs, and much more.

The full list of features:
- Adds GTALens links on users' profiles pages (you must be authenticated on RGSC for links to appear);
- Adds GTALens jobs links on https://socialclub.rockstargames.com/jobs;
- Adds GTALens jobs links on job pages (even for deleted ones!);
- Finally, it removes the age verification popup!
